DATA SOURCES
============

This application aggregates data from the following public sources:

1. Congress-Legislators Dataset
   Source: https://github.com/unitedstates/congress-legislators
   License: CC0 1.0 Universal (Public Domain)
   Maintained by: unitedstates project contributors

2. Congress.gov API
   Source: https://api.congress.gov/
   Provider: Library of Congress
   Terms: https://www.congress.gov/about/policies

3. Federal Election Commission (FEC) API
   Source: https://api.open.fec.gov/
   Provider: Federal Election Commission
   Terms: https://www.fec.gov/data/legal/requirements/

4. U.S. Census Bureau API
   Source: https://www.census.gov/data/developers.html
   Provider: U.S. Census Bureau
   Terms: https://www.census.gov/data/developers/about/terms-of-service.html

5. GDELT Project
   Source: https://www.gdeltproject.org/
   Provider: GDELT
   License: Data is provided free for research and non-commercial use

6. OpenStates API (Planned for Phase 2)
   Source: https://openstates.org/
   Provider: OpenStates
   License: Data under Open Database License (ODbL)

GOVERNMENT DATA DISCLAIMER
==========================

All government data used in this application remains in the public domain.
This application does not claim any ownership over government data.
